title: VIDEO CATNIP.iso
description:
Video Catnip is a looping video of birds and squirrels in the park that will drive your cats insane.  Make sure you clear the top of your TV off as they like to perch on top to try and catch the birds.  Crank the audio too so they won't know where the birds are.  It's a crazy simple video that I wish I'd thought of.

No details on encoding or anything.  It's not worth it.  Just download it for your cat.  You'll be glad you did!
